            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns">
               <h3 class="hclass5">Mike</h3>
               <p class="pclass3">a.k.a. Dad</p>
               <p>Mike is a twenty-five+ year veteran of the grocery and mass retail industries. Various management positions in store operations, advertising, sales and marketing, transportation and logistics, and general maintenance. His love of food and cooking make him an invaluable member of the McClure's leadership team. Semi-retired in 2006 he assists Bob and Joe in their endeavors with the business. As McClure's continues to grow his favorite thing to do, even after 30 years of doing it, is still to "put 'em in the jar."</p>
            </div>
